('fd235e0b-928c-4539-a7c3-602734cf5626', 'Annual Cariari Charity Gala', 'Join us for an elegant evening of dining, dancing, and fundraising for the local youth center. Black-tie optional.', now() + interval '30 days', now() + interval '30 days 5 hours', 'Cariari Country Club Ballroom', 'https://placeholdr.ai/06ede577-32f3-4e0a-a17d-14073e441cce/512/512', 'Other'),
